formBody: An unplanned event is a event that happened without preparation. Of your 4 planned or unplanned CPDs at most 2 of them can be unplanned.

questionGroups.title: Describe an unplanned learning opportunity and the outcome.

questions.title: Describe an unplanned event of activity that enabled you to learn something new or refresh your knowledge or skills.
Give an example of how this learning benefited your patients or service users.
